Rating: 4
This was delicious, and the presentation was very attractive. I used a bag of frozen artichoke hearts and simmered them in the broth for just a few minutes, which was easier and cheaper but tasted great. Also, reduced butter to 1 Tbs. and added a bit of truffle oil to potatoes, which flavored them very nicely. Used a golden balsalmic because I thought the color and flavor would be better. Fantastic recipe for a special dinner!

